        {
            "title": "Barclays研究標普500在寬鬆週期逆轉時的歷史表現",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/a6RCAuwenlClVnuZ1wBDBw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEABU081_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Barclays\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Barclays;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Barclays\">Barclays</a>於週五向客戶發布的研究報告中，深入分析了標普500在聯邦儲備局（Fed）結束降息週期、重啟升息時的歷史表現，結果發現：在升息逆轉發生之前，市場所受的阻力相當有限，但在首次升息之後，股市回報往往趨於低迷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Venu Krishna指出，在最新通脹數據公布後，市場目前已將Fed於年底前重啟升息的預期納入定價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Barclays梳理了過去數十年間，Fed共五次逆轉寬鬆政策的典型案例——即在完成一輪降息週期、維持利率不變一段時間後，重新啟動升息。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-863e3179-e4f0-39c0-8f89-92b2afd71b7c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在大多數情況下，Barclays發現，即將到來的政策逆轉「在事件發生前6個月內，並未對標普500的回報構成重大阻力」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而，首次升息落地後，情況明顯轉變。Barclays表示，此後股市的表現「通常相當低迷，平均出現低個位數的跌幅」，在升息後兩週至三個月的觀察窗口內，五次案例中有三至四次錄得下跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述研究結果正值投資者密切關注通脹數據超預期後、新一輪升息週期重啟的可能性之際。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Barclays的歷史分析顯示，儘管政策轉向前的醞釀期未必會拖累股市表現，但首次升息後的一段時間，歷史上往往是標普500面臨回調風險較高的時期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/barclays%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE500%E5%9C%A8%E5%AF%AC%E9%AC%86%E9%80%B1%E6%9C%9F%E9%80%86%E8%BD%89%E6%99%82%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE-141744365.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-06-12 22:30:51",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "〈美股早盤〉受伊朗核協議預期和SpaceX IPO提振 標普、道瓊上漲",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mQUBPpTeX2g9QxblOSp0bA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/f61cb7ac8276b1f526af952fa1ef190f\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
